channel.title: My server
channel.description:
Well i saw weedscape being advertised so i thought id advertise my server because theres usually only 5-10 people online when there used to be 30-40, after server has been down for about a month, anyway heres some features:
Chaos Elemental - pretty similar one to real rs apart from it only removes weapons sometimes rather than teleport you to random squares near it When you get hit you do the block emote (different for certain weapons) Alot of weapons have their own walking, running and attacking emotes (like when you run with a whip it trails behind you like on rs2, and when you run with karils bow you hold it against your stomach sorta, also like rs2) Goes from morning to afternoon, from afternoon to evening, from evening to night, from night to morning according to GMT time, and every 20 minutes randomly changes weather to either snowing, sandstorm, or just normal. Friendlist which saves Magic on npcs Food working again Two fully working quests Full clues almost as good as real rs (only difference is there is no mages that attack you on certain clues) Ancient magicks - first server to have them Normal magic - only entangle, but working on a quest for god spells and ill also be adding teleblock soon Ranged - works, stand still while firing Graphics - for ice blocks n stuff Graphics handler - makes them show for everyone
Coming soon:
More quests Magic bugs fixed (works but on blood spells instead of healing you it damages you for some reason) MOVING GRAPHICS (arrows and things like ice blocks on ancient magicks, im fairly close and i keep having to bribe swift for more clues on getting closer and kenetix is helping me, i cant promise this soon though)
Ip is cheezscape.servegame.org - usually daily updates unless i get bored of servers, which is rarely, and also itll be up around 5-10 hours a day
Site is http://cheezscape.ath.cx:8080/cheezscape/
Status:
617 forum members 8995 savegames Most players ever online (not bugged): around 160
